				<div type="textpart" subtype="book">
				<ab><title><ref target="http://www.dfhg-project.org/DFHG/index.php?volume=Volumen quartum#urn:lofts:fhg.4.melito.melitonis_fragmenta.de_atheniensium_gentibus.e_libro_primo">
